{"pid":"c0185e27697245bd788e8535c96d05ec99533f11","tid":143383,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"買水波爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c63ac88fab9e318e44fb2b87d98c06c62ad8baf","tid":143383,"uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買水波爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328439aa917cac4b5c6560bd6cee415c86c0e120","tid":143383,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有位就嵌入式，好似外國果d<br />\n大部d 好力d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有用緊？<br />\n我就煩緊壞左點<br />\n一係要換 拆又煩<br />\n一係要比錢整 又可能整唔番</blockquote><br />\n我係香港有座枱式<br />\n果時英國讀書用嵌入式<br />\n<br />\n嵌入式係warm up 同埋整熟d 肉快d<br />\n座枱式慳位囉，不過好慢，d 肉厚d 中間有時會唔熟<br />\n<br />\n如果整就嵌入式點都麻煩d, 有d 零件係機後面<br />\n就好似洗衣機乾衣機咁<br />\n座枱式整唔掂就換過部都好平<br />\n但你新買應該有幾年保養既"},{"pid":"402bc780648511c26187ef19d552d73506683376","tid":143383,"uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有位就嵌入式，好似外國果d<br />\n大部d 好力d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有用緊？<br />\n我就煩緊壞左點<br />\n一係要換 拆又煩<br />\n一係要比錢整 又可能整唔番</blockquote><br />\n我係香港有座枱式<br />\n果時英國讀書用嵌入式<br />\n<br />\n嵌入式係warm up 同埋整熟d 肉快d<br />\n座枱式慳位囉，不過好慢，d 肉厚d 中間有時會唔熟<br />\n<br />\n如果整就嵌入式點都麻煩d, 有d 零件係機後面<br />\n就好似洗衣機乾衣機咁<br />\n座枱式整唔掂就換過部都好平<br />\n但你新買應該有幾年保養既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n座枱係咪都整到雞魚果啲？<br />\n你座枱同嵌入用過咩牌子有咩comment啊？"},{"pid":"dcdc0dad631c12a8959983c0b4252227b89a7b9a","tid":143383,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買水波爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" 